Constraints:
  - 0 <= number of nodes <= 5000
  - -1000 <= Node.val <= 1000
  - -1000 <= targetSum <= 1000

Hint:
  DFS with a current path array and remaining sum.
  At each node: push node.val to path, subtract from remaining.
